Provided with it and accompanied by the Sibyl, he reaches the entrance to the infernal regions ( 1 56- 336). On the hither side of the Styx he meets with the shade of his quondam pilot Palinurus, and after receiving from him 3 detailed account of the circumstances attending his death, he promises to perform to him the due obsequias on his return to earth, and to erect a cenotaph (337- 383).
